## Throttle Proxy

A lightweight Go reverse proxy that protects upstream services from request floods.

* GitHub: https://github.com/spaghetti-coder/throttle-proxy
* Features:
  - Request serialization (max one in-flight per upstream)
  - EDF scheduling across multiple upstreams
  - Automatic delay escalation under sustained load
  - Round-robin passthrough for non-throttled endpoints
  - Upstream health tracking with automatic failover

